Package: saytime-weather-rb
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ruby (>= 2.7.0), asl3-asterisk
Description: Time and weather announcement system for Asterisk
 A time and weather announcement system for Asterisk PBX, designed for radio
 systems, repeater controllers, and amateur radio applications.
 .
 Features:
  * Time announcements in 12-hour or 24-hour formats
  * Worldwide weather via postal codes, ICAO airport codes, or special locations
  * No API keys required - uses free weather APIs
  * Location-aware timezone support
 .
 Zero external dependencies - uses only Ruby standard library.

